            <span>Redes Sociales Plan Básico (3 meses):</span>
            <span class="font-medium">$612.000</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-ink/80 border-b border-hairline-soft pb-2">
            <span>Descuento paquete (5%):</span>
